title: Test
summary: This is a multi-line chart with 2 lines representing Establishments, and Employees.
The line for Employees has the highest values across Year with a mean value of 148.0,
and it peaked at 2007 with a value of 184.0.
Establishments mostly had the least y-axis name with a mean value of 6.58,
which peaked at 2007 with a value of 9.3.
Establishments reported the lowest y-axis name  about 4.5 in Year 2008
Overall Employees is gradually decreasing, Establishments is roughly constant,  throughout the Year
The difference of y_axis name between Establishments and Employees is smaller at Year 2009 compared to the Year 2006.
The greatest difference of y_axis name between Establishments and Employees occurs at Year 2007 and the smallest difference occurs at 2009.
